Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有点颠簸\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Bumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这肯定是我最后一次上飞机了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}This is the last time I ever get on a plane again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要是死了 琼就成孤儿了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}If we die, June will be an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:02:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她会照顾好自己的\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}She'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}It's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,丹巴 法罗岛\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Faro, Damba.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:47.54,comment,,0,0,0,,丹巴为法罗岛伯格曼私人影院的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,丹 巴\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}D-A-M-B-A.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,门牌号呢\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}House number?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,2078
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,出发\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,您将在一小时\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}You will reach your destination
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,四十八分钟后到达目的地\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}in one hour, 48 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,两百米后\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}In 200 meters,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在斯卡夫克斯哥顿左转\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}turn left on "Skarfolksgaten,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在奇尔瓦街右转\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}then you will turn right on "Chilvarvejen."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一百米后\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}In 100 meters,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在奇尔瓦维简街左转\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}turn left on "Skarfolksgaten."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我没加任何新的外景地\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}No, I didn't add any new locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那间赌场是一开始就有的\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}The casino was there in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 行 兄弟 - 实际上 原来有两处\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Yeah, okay, bud. - In fact, there were two of them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我给他削减成一间了 如果这\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}and I cut it down to one, so if this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们的问题是 心理细节和描写太少了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}If their problem is that there's not enough psychological detail or description,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那很简单 我们就再搞个角色出来 他们整合进去\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}then it's easy, we just find someone and they put it back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们来整合进去 行吧 - 我觉得他们想把拍摄再推迟一个月\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- They put it back in, right?- I think they'd like to push the shoot back another month,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们还有时间想想怎么办\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}so we've got time to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们要推迟的话 可能会有一半演员跑路\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Yeah, well, if they push, they're gonna lose half the cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们知道这点吧\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}They know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一百米后 进入法罗路 靠右行驶\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}In 100 meters, on "Farovejen," stay to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,靠右行驶\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Stay to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我要下去\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我把太阳镜掉在机场了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}I think I left my sunglasses at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一百米后 您将到达目的地\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}In 100 meters, you will reach your destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那一定就是她了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Oh, that has got to be her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们没迷路 - 导航的功劳\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- You didn't get lost.- Miracle of GPS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好 因为这里没人会帮你们\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Ah, good, because no one here would have helped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,法罗人跟伯格曼之间\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}There is a secret pact between the people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有一项秘密协定 - 很高兴知道\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- of Faro and Bergman.- Good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 奥瑟 很高兴认识你 - 托尼 我也是\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Ase, nice to meet you.- Tony. And you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 奥瑟 - 克丽斯\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Ase.- Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我负责照料房子\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}I take care of the houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这很漂亮\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很迷人 - 是啊\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Yeah, it's gorgeous.- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在那栋房子里 有伯格曼的私人影院\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}In that house, you'll find Bergman's private screening room,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以看到35毫米胶片版本的放映\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}where you can see 35mm prints
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在伯格曼周的时候\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}during Bergman Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以免费使用自行车\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}You're free to use the bicycles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真好\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Oh. Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们想去劳特尔\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}And if you want to go to Lauter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,造访伯格曼的家\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}to visit Bergman's home,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,骑自行车十分钟就到\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}it's a 10-minute bike ride from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是客厅\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}This is the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这个电视 很老很老了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}And this TV, it's very, very old,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:08:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但还能用\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}but it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是卡比拉瑞忒的钢琴\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}This was Kabi Laretei's piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他的第四任妻子\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}His fourth wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个优秀的钢琴家\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}She was a great pianist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看得出来 这个地方很适合工作\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}You'll see, this place is perfect for working.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这是栋陈设简单的房子\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}It's a very simple house,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,便于居住\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}easy to live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,卧室在楼上\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}The bedrooms are upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,大的那间是 婚姻生活 的取景地\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}The big one was in Scenes From A Marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那部让几百万人离了婚的电影\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}the film that made millions of people divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我还得带你们看下垃圾怎么处理\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Oh, I have to show you for the garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞典人对循环利用可不是开玩笑的\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}In Sweden, we are very serious about recycling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想的话我也可以去别的地方\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}I can go somewhere else if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,克丽斯\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Chris?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,克丽斯\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-克丽丝 -托尼\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Chris!- Tony!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在磨坊这里\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Over here in the mill!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在哪呢 - 嗨\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Where are you?- Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我就在这安家了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}I think I'll be setting up in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以互相挥手\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}We can wave at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得这有点太好了吗\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}But don't you think it's too nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,过于\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,过于什么\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Too what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,过于美丽\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切宁静 如此完美\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}All this calm and perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现有些压抑\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}I find it oppressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不啊 还挺放松的\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}No. It's soothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想不出来\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Yeah,but I didn't realize,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 在这里写作\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}you know, writing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎样才会不觉得自己是个输家呢\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}how can I not feel like a loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至怕坐在桌子面前\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}I'm even afraid to sit at a desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去外面写\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Well, write outside, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人来这里工作的\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}A lot of people come here to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,学生 作家 设计师\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}students, writers, designers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可没人在期待写出一部 假面\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}No one's expecting Persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那真是谢天谢地了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Yeah, well, thank God for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定意识到\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}You do realize
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要睡在\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}we're going to sleep in the bed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们拍婚姻生活的那张床上吧\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}where they shot Scenes From A Marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那部让几百万人离了婚的电影\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}"The film that made millions of people divorce."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道 - 也许我们得睡去另外一间\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- I know.- We have to maybe sleep in the other bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,分床睡\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Separate beds?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,玩得开心\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 托尼 - 你好 很高兴认识你\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Tony.- Hello. Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很高兴认识你 - 这是克丽丝\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Nice to see you.- This is Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:12:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好 克丽丝 -你好\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Hi, Chris.- Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是海达\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}And this is Hedda,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,伯格曼基金会的主管\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}who's the head of the Bergman Foundation.
