Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.11,0:24:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.82,0:24:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他的角色总是这么糟糕呢\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Why are his characters always so awful?
