Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.63,1:40:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,锁上门 把钥匙放在门旁的盒子里\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}lock up and put the key in the box near the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.13,1:40:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吗 - 好\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Okay?- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.77,1:41:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 安德斯 - 嗨 克丽丝\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Hi, Anders.- Hey, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.98,1:41:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有一秒 我不知道我在哪了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}For a second, I didn't know where I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.77,1:41:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都混了起来\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Everything was mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.11,1:41:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,剧组走了 我以为你也走了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}The crew left. So, I thought you'd gone too.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.82,1:41:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我累了 我需要躺一会\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}I was tired. I... I needed to lie down.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.11,1:41:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我们都累坏了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Yeah, we're all exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.66,1:41:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但拍摄几乎结束了 - 对\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- But the shoot is almost over.- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.28,1:41:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚到吗\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}You just got here?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.33,1:41:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我在看你拍今天的最后一幕\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}No, I was watching you doing the last shot of the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.33,1:41:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想没看伯格曼的房子\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}I didn't want to leave the island
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.92,1:41:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就离开这座岛\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}without seeing Bergman's house.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.88,1:41:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,说真的 你可以为我在这里写一幕\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Seriously, you could have written a scene for me here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.76,1:41:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我试过了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}I tried.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.72,1:41:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,只是你的角色没理由来这里\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}There was simply no reason for your character to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.31,1:41:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快五点了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Oh. It's almost five.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.97,1:41:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得在马车变成南瓜之前\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}We have to leave before the carriage
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.94,1:41:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧离开\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}turns into a pumpkin.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.56,1:41:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你能先带我看看图书馆吗\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Will you show me the library first?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.77,1:41:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.32,1:41:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着我\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.99,1:42:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一辈子都不够我\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}An entire life wouldn't be enough time
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.78,1:42:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这里四分之一的书\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}for me to read one-quarter of these books.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.71,1:42:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我在这里最喜欢的东西\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}This is my favorite object here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.33,1:42:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这是Dramaten的模型\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}It's a model of the Dramaten,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.83,1:42:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,斯德哥尔摩皇家剧院\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}the national theater of Stockholm.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.92,1:42:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,当伯格曼离开时送给他的\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}It was given to Bergman when he left.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.51,1:42:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁在他最喜欢的位置上偷看呢\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}And who is in his favorite position spying?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.02,1:42:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,英格玛伯格曼\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Ingmar Bergman.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.47,1:43:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,现在有车要去信天翁镇 如果有人感兴趣的话\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}There's a car leaving for Albatross, if anyone's interested.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.68,1:43:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Me!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.14,1:43:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 这就是告别了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}So, this is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.48,1:43:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我明天一早就走\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Yeah, I'm off early tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.40,1:43:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你妻子和孩子会在机场等你\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}I guess your wife and kid will be waiting at the airport?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.65,1:43:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我最好在斯德哥尔摩找到点好礼物\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Yeah. I'd better find some nice presents in Stockholm,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.03,1:43:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我可能要搭第一班飞机回来了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}or I might as well take the first plane back.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.53,1:43:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你总可以买羔羊皮的\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Well, you can always get sheepskins.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.49,1:43:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜 - 好好的\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Bye.- Be well.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.37,1:43:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一路顺风 - 拜\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Safe travels.- Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.33,1:43:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,明天见\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.17,1:43:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 最后玩把游戏\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}So, one last game?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.63,1:43:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.13,1:43:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再抽根烟我们就走\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}One cigarette and we'll go.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.97,1:43:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 继续玩啊 - 他妈别想\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Back to the stable.- No fucking way.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.69,1:43:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨这个游戏 我们能别玩了吗\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}I hate this game. Can we stop it, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.85,1:43:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就承认你不喜欢输吧\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Just admit that you don't like losing.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.02,1:44:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你不喜欢事物脱离掌控的感觉\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}You don't like it when things escape you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.03,1:44:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我需要心理医生的话 你肯定会是我最\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}If I needed a shrink, you'd be the last...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.70,1:44:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,第二最不想见的\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}you'd be the second last person I'd go see.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.00,1:44:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁是最不想的 - 我妈\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Who'd be the last?- My mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.08,1:44:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,操\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Oh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.33,1:44:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 停吧\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Okay, enough. Let's stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.54,1:44:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这个游戏 太滑稽了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}This game is, uh, ridiculous,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.29,1:44:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我也真的需要睡点觉\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}and I really need to get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.17,1:44:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,预计离出发还有四个小时\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Estimated time of departure in four hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.15,1:44:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你不来说再见吗\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}You're not coming to say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.86,1:44:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我被卡住了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}I'm stuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.18,1:45:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你做的一切\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.06,1:45:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,别谢我\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Please don't thank me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.61,1:45:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要睡点觉\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}You should get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.65,1:45:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,明天得像个人样\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}You have to be in shape tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.20,1:45:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 走吧\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Go on, get going.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.16,1:46:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 想去看一眼吗 - 好\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Wanna go take a look? - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.93,1:46:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 你知道这座岛 还挺特别的 对吧\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}So, you know this island.I t's kind a special right?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.72,1:46:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,对 这就是那个你和妈妈\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Yeah. It's the island of the director
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.93,1:46:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 都很喜欢的导演住的岛 - 对 没错\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- you and Mommy like a lot.- Yep. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.18,1:46:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他活着还是死了 - 他死了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Is he alive or dead?- He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.98,1:46:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他上天堂了吗\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Did he go to heaven?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.90,1:46:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,值得怀疑\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Mmm. Questionable.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.48,1:46:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,爸 有件事我想问你\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Dad, there's something I really want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.90,1:46:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 说吧那 - 鬼魂真的存在吗\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Go on then.- Do ghosts really exist?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.49,1:46:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 存在 - 跟我说真话\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Yes.- Tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.91,1:46:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那不\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}No?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.24,1:46:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们存在 - 或者不\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Yes, they do!- Or they don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.50,1:47:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么要讲鬼故事呢\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Then why do you tell ghost stories?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.79,1:47:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我 - 奶奶说你\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}- Moi?- Grandma said you were
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.84,1:47:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要拍一部有鬼魂的故事\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}going to make a movie with ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.88,1:47:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶说的 是吧 她怎么知道的\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Oh, Grandma said that, did she? What does she know?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.96,1:47:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她在网上读到的\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}She read it on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.30,1:47:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在还上网了 是吧\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Oh, she's on the internet now, is she?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.93,1:47:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你能告诉我你的鬼故事吗\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Yeah. Can you tell me your ghost story?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.64,1:47:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个僵尸的故事\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}It's a zombie story, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.22,1:47:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,僵尸 还有怪兽\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Zombies. And there's this monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.10,1:47:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这个大怪兽\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}This gigantic, like...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.15,1:47:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,蘑菇从他的屁股里长出来\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}mushrooms coming out of his bum,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.40,1:47:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,像爆炸的耳朵\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}like exploding ears,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.07,1:47:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,还沾满了大便\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}plus, covered in poo.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.78,1:47:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,从头到脚\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}From top to bottom, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.91,1:47:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还有血从他的耳朵里流出来\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}And blood bleeding from his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.24,1:47:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-- 还有一个巨人女孩 - 好\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&} And there's a giant girl.- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.48,1:48:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.77,1:48:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你到那上面去\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}If you go up there
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.98,1:48:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,努力地找的话 我想你可以找到你妈\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}and you look real hard, I think you might find your mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.82,1:48:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 去找找\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Go on, go for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.43,1:48:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,琼\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}June!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.77,1:48:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我的宝贝\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Oh, my baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.44,1:48:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的宝宝\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Mmm, my love.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.31,1:49:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,谁能无风便起航\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Who can sail without the wind?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.27,1:49:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,谁能无桨去划行\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Who can row without an oar?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.57,1:49:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,谁能跟挚爱告别\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}Who can say goodbye to their love...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.37,1:49:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,却不流泪\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}without crying?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.84,1:49:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我能无风便起航\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}I can sail without the wind.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.39,1:50:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我也能无桨去划行\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}And I can row without an oar.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.43,1:50:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不能跟挚爱告别\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}But I can't say goodbye to my love...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.44,1:50:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,却不流泪\N{\fs35\1c&H62A8EB&}without crying.

